# === Geneso nft-web — copy to .env ===
#
# 1) Deploy contracts from repo `contracts/` (see contracts/README.md) on the SAME
#    network as in src/web3/config.ts (currently Ethereum mainnet, chainId 1).
# 2) Put deployed addresses here and restart `npm run dev`.
# 3) Wallet: MetaMask (or another injected wallet) on Ethereum mainnet, with ETH for gas.
# 4) To create listings: set collection address, own an NFT from that collection,
#    then Approve marketplace + createListing (UI on Discover page).
# 5) Optional: WalletConnect for mobile — create a project at https://cloud.walletconnect.com

VITE_MARKETPLACE_ADDRESS=0xYourMarketplaceAddress
VITE_NFT_COLLECTION_ADDRESS=0xYourNftCollectionAddress

# VITE_WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID=
